    • Method Detail

      • getMessages

        public MessageCacheItem getMessages()
        Get MessageCacheItem from cache. The cache is refreshed if MessageCacheItem is expired or not found. Pre-configured locale fallback queue is used on failure.
        Returns:
        A MessageCacheItem whose message map is one of the items in the following priority-ordered list:
        • The messages in the requested locale
        • The messages in a default locale
        • The source messages
        • An empty map

      • getMessages

        public MessageCacheItem getMessages​(java.util.Iterator<java.util.Locale> fallbackLocalesIter)
        Get MessageCacheItem from cache. The cache is refreshed if MessageCacheItem is expired or not found.
        Parameters:
        fallbackLocalesIter - The locale fallback queue to be used on failure. If null, there will be no fallback mechanism on failure so the message map will be empty.
        Returns:
        A MessageCacheItem whose data map is one of the following:
        • The messages in the requested locale
        • The messages in a fallback locale
